{"title":"Git 版控整合 - JGit 筆記","uid":"8ccce8f3a4385f7644b3a42e45ef427e","slug":"jgit-notes","date":"2023-01-24T12:19:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-30T08:30:20.329Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/jgit-notes.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/xN9DEqZ.jpg","content":"<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xN9DEqZ.jpg\" alt=\"cover\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"匯入函式庫\"><a href=\"#匯入函式庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"匯入函式庫\"></a>匯入函式庫</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-gradle\" data-language=\"gradle\"><code class=\"language-gradle\">implementation &#39;org.eclipse.jgit:org.eclipse.jgit:$version&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"基本慨念\"><a href=\"#基本慨念\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本慨念\"></a>基本慨念</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>原文網址：<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://kknews.cc/code/gpxmnvl.html\">https://kknews.cc/code/gpxmnvl.html</a></p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Git 對象（Git Objects）：就是 git 的對象。它們在 git 中用 SHA-1 來表示。在 JGit 中用 <code>AnyObjectId</code> 和 <code>ObjectId</code> 表示。而它又包含了四種類型：<ul>\n<li>二進位大對象（<code>blob</code>）</li>\n<li>文件數據樹（<code>tree</code>）</li>\n<li>指向其它的 <code>tree</code> 和 <code>blob</code> 提交（<code>commit</code>）</li>\n<li>指向某一棵 <code>tree</code> 標籤（<code>tag</code>）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>引用（<code>Ref</code>）：對某一個 git 對象的引用。</li>\n<li>倉庫（<code>Repository</code>）：顧名思義，就是用於存儲所有 git 對象和 <code>Ref</code> 的倉庫。</li>\n<li>RevWalk：該類用於從 <code>commit</code> 的關係圖（graph）中遍歷 <code>commit</code>。</li>\n<li>RevCommit：表示一個 git 的 <code>commit</code></li>\n<li>RevTag：表示一個 git 的 <code>tag</code></li>\n<li>RevTree：表示一個 git 的 <code>tree</code></li>\n<li>TreeWalk：類似 RevWalk，但是用於遍歷一棵 <code>tree</code></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"基本存儲庫操作\"><a href=\"#基本存儲庫操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本存儲庫操作\"></a>基本存儲庫操作</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"Git-控制處理源文件\"><a href=\"#Git-控制處理源文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Git 控制處理源文件\"></a>Git 控制處理源文件</h2><p>我們會另建一個類別 <code>GitControl.java</code> 來彈性使用。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"定義所需變量\"><a href=\"#定義所需變量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定義所需變量\"></a>定義所需變量</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">private String localPath, remotePath;\nprivate String username &#x3D; &quot;username&quot;, password &#x3D; &quot;password&quot;;\nprivate String token &#x3D; &quot;&quot;;\nprivate Git git;\nprivate Repository localRepo;\nprivate CredentialsProvider credentialsProvider;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"初始化-Git-控制\"><a href=\"#初始化-Git-控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化 Git 控制\"></a>初始化 Git 控制</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public GitControl(String localPath, String remotePath) &#123;\n    this.localPath &#x3D; localPath;\n    this.remotePath &#x3D; remotePath;\n\n    try &#123;\n        this.localRepo &#x3D; new FileRepository(localPath + &quot;&#x2F;.git&quot;);\n    &#125; catch (IOException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n\n    credentialsProvider &#x3D; new UsernamePasswordCredentialsProvider(this.username, this.password);\n    git &#x3D; new Git(localRepo);\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"克隆遠端存儲庫至本地端\"><a href=\"#克隆遠端存儲庫至本地端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"克隆遠端存儲庫至本地端\"></a>克隆遠端存儲庫至本地端</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void cloneRepo() &#123;\n    try &#123;\n        Git.cloneRepository()\n                .setURI(remotePath)\n                .setDirectory(new File(localPath))\n                .call();\n    &#125; catch (GitAPIException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"抓取遠端存儲庫之檔案至本地端\"><a href=\"#抓取遠端存儲庫之檔案至本地端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"抓取遠端存儲庫之檔案至本地端\"></a>抓取遠端存儲庫之檔案至本地端</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void pullFromRepo()&#123;\n    try &#123;\n        git.pull().call();\n    &#125; catch (GitAPIException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"新增檔案至遠端存儲庫\"><a href=\"#新增檔案至遠端存儲庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新增檔案至遠端存儲庫\"></a>新增檔案至遠端存儲庫</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void addToRepo() &#123;\n    try &#123;\n        git.add().addFilepattern(&quot;.&quot;).call();\n    &#125; catch (GitAPIException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"提交檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\"><a href=\"#提交檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"提交檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\"></a>提交檔案變更至遠端存儲庫</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void commitToRepo(String message) &#123;\n    try &#123;\n        git.commit().setMessage(message).call();\n    &#125; catch (GitAPIException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"推送檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\"><a href=\"#推送檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"推送檔案變更至遠端存儲庫\"></a>推送檔案變更至遠端存儲庫</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public void pushToRepo()&#123;\n    git.push().setCredentialsProvider(credentialsProvider)\n            .setForce(true)\n            .setPushAll();\n    Iterator&lt;PushResult&gt; it &#x3D; null;\n\n    try &#123;\n        it &#x3D; git.push().call().iterator();\n    &#125; catch (GitAPIException e) &#123;\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    &#125;\n\n    if (it.hasNext()) &#123;\n        String str &#x3D; it.next().toString();\n        Toast.makeText(App.getContext(), str, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"使用方式\"><a href=\"#使用方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用方式\"></a>使用方式</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">&#x2F;&#x2F; example\nvar localPath &#x3D; Environment.getExternalStorageDirectory().toString() + &quot;&#x2F;GitTest&#x2F;MyDir&#x2F;&quot;;\nvar remotePath &#x3D; &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;XXX&#x2F;YYY.git&quot;;\n\nGitControl gc &#x3D; new GitControl(localPath, remotePath);\n\ngc.cloneRepo();\ngc.addToRepo();\ngc.commitToRepo(&quot;First commit&quot;);\ngc.pushToRepo();\ngc.pullFromRepo();</code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"疑難雜症\"><a href=\"#疑難雜症\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"疑難雜症\"></a>疑難雜症</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"Unauthorized-錯誤\"><a href=\"#Unauthorized-錯誤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Unauthorized 錯誤\"></a>Unauthorized 錯誤</h2><p>可能性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>存儲庫是私有的。</li>\n<li>你沒建立 Personal Access Token。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"NoSuchMethodError-錯誤\"><a href=\"#NoSuchMethodError-錯誤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NoSuchMethodError 錯誤\"></a>NoSuchMethodError 錯誤</h2><p>JGit 6.3.x 版本起，開始使用了 <code>OutputStream</code> 類別中的一個函數 <code>transferTo()</code>，這個方法是 <strong>Android 13 版本新加入的</strong>。如果在低於 Android 13 版本中使用 <code>transferTo()</code> 方面，會導致 <code>NoSuchMethodError</code>，因為找不到該方法，程式跳掉。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-log\" data-language=\"log\"><code class=\"language-log\">java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: No virtual method transferTo(Ljava&#x2F;io&#x2F;OutputStream;)J in class Ljava&#x2F;io&#x2F;InputStream; or its super classes (declaration of &#39;java.io.InputStream&#39; appears in &#x2F;apex&#x2F;com.android.art&#x2F;javalib&#x2F;core-oj.jar)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.dircache.DirCacheCheckout.getContent(DirCacheCheckout.java:1684)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.dircache.DirCacheCheckout.getContent(DirCacheCheckout.java:1609)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.dircache.DirCacheCheckout.checkoutEntry(DirCacheCheckout.java:1535)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.dircache.DirCacheCheckout.doCheckout(DirCacheCheckout.java:569)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.dircache.DirCacheCheckout.checkout(DirCacheCheckout.java:471)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.api.CloneCommand.checkout(CloneCommand.java:399)\n    at org.eclipse.jgit.api.CloneCommand.call(CloneCommand.java:220)\n    ...</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"NetworkOnMainThreadException-錯誤\"><a href=\"#NetworkOnMainThreadException-錯誤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NetworkOnMainThreadException 錯誤\"></a>NetworkOnMainThreadException 錯誤</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;uses-permission android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.permission.INTERNET&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n&lt;uses-permission android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>The exception that is thrown when an application attempts to perform a networking operation on its main thread.</p>\n<p>This is only thrown for applications targeting the Honeycomb SDK or higher. Applications targeting <strong>earlier SDK versions are allowed to do networking on their main event loop threads, but it’s heavily discouraged</strong>.</p></blockquote>\n<p>這個是 Android 系統原生的機制，如果應用程式<strong>嘗試在主執行緒中請求網絡程序</strong>，將會出現這個錯誤，這用以<strong>防止網絡請求逾時而導致界面響應變慢，甚至無法操作的狀態的情況發生</strong>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"方法-1-強制禁用執行緒嚴格政策（不推薦使用）\"><a href=\"#方法-1-強制禁用執行緒嚴格政策（不推薦使用）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法 1 - 強制禁用執行緒嚴格政策（不推薦使用）\"></a>方法 1 - 強制禁用執行緒嚴格政策（不推薦使用）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">StrictMode.ThreadPolicy policy &#x3D; new StrictMode.ThreadPolicy.Builder().permitAll().build();\nStrictMode.setThreadPolicy(policy);</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>只適用於<strong>網絡請求數據量很小</strong>的時候使用。</p>\n\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"方法-2-使用異步執行緒-AsyncTask\"><a href=\"#方法-2-使用異步執行緒-AsyncTask\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法 2 - 使用異步執行緒 AsyncTask\"></a>方法 2 - 使用異步執行緒 AsyncTask</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class NetworkTask extends AsyncTask&lt;String, Void, String&gt; &#123;\n\n    protected String doInBackground(String... urls) &#123;\n        &#x2F;&#x2F; ...\n        return $result; &#x2F;&#x2F; returns the data fetched from the network\n    &#125;\n\n    protected void onPostExecute(String result) &#123;\n        &#x2F;&#x2F; ...\n    &#125;\n\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Operation-Not-permitted-錯誤\"><a href=\"#Operation-Not-permitted-錯誤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Operation Not permitted 錯誤\"></a>Operation Not permitted 錯誤</h2><p>你要為應用程式開啟<strong>所有檔案存取</strong>權限。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;uses-permission android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n&lt;uses-permission android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n&lt;uses-permission android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.permission.MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<p>簡單記錄一下 JGit 的筆記。</p>\n","text":" 原文網址：https://kknews.cc/code/gpxmnvl.html Git 對象（Git Objects）：就是 git 的對象。它們在 git 中用 SHA-1 來表示。在 JGit 中用 和 表示。而它又包含了四種類型： 二進位大對象（） 文件數據樹（） 指向...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.9k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android 開發","slug":"Android-開發","count":11,"path":"api/categories/Android-開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":11,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8C%AF%E5%85%A5%E5%87%BD%E5%BC%8F%E5%BA%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">匯入函式庫</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%85%A8%E5%BF%B5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本慨念</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%98%E5%84%B2%E5%BA%AB%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本存儲庫操作</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Git-%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E6%BA%90%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Git 控制處理源文件</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\